01:14:05,827 --> 01:14:09,087
which is basically what
part of Star Wars is about.

1188
01:14:09,157 --> 01:14:10,887
The circle is now complete.

1189
01:14:11,367 --> 01:14:13,527
When I left you,
I was but the learner.

1190
01:14:13,597 --> 01:14:15,627
Now I am the master.

